@using System.Text.Encodings.Web
@inject UrlEncoder MyUrlEncoder
@model NamEcommerce.Web.Contracts.Models.Orders.OrderListModel
@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Quản lý Đơn hàng";
    
    string GetStatusBadgeClass(int status) => status switch
    {
        0 => "bg-secondary",   // Pending
        1 => "bg-primary",     // Processing
        2 => "bg-success",     // Completed
        3 => "bg-danger",      // Cancelled
        _ => "bg-dark"
    };

    string GetStatusText(int status) => status switch
    {
        0 => "Đang chờ",
        1 => "Đang xử lý",
        2 => "Hoàn thành",
        3 => "Đã hủy",
        _ => "Không xác định"
    };

    string GetPaymentStatusBadgeClass(int status) => status switch
    {
        0 => "bg-warning",   // Pending
        1 => "bg-success",   // Paid
        2 => "bg-info",      // Refunded
        _ => "bg-dark"
    };

    string GetPaymentStatusText(int status) => status switch
    {
        0 => "Chưa Thu",
        1 => "Đã Thu",
        2 => "Hoàn Tiền",
        _ => "KXĐ"
    };

    string GetShippingStatusBadgeClass(int status) => status switch
    {
        0 => "bg-secondary", // Pending
        1 => "bg-primary",   // Shipping
        2 => "bg-success",   // Delivered
        3 => "bg-danger",    // Returned
        _ => "bg-dark"
    };

    string GetShippingStatusText(int status) => status switch
    {
        0 => "Chưa Giao",
        1 => "Đang Giao",
        2 => "Đã Giao",
        3 => "Trả Lại",
        _ => "KXĐ"
    };

    var query = Model.Keywords;
    
    var successMessage = TempData[ViewConstants.OrderSuccessMessage] as string;
    var errorMessage = TempData[ViewConstants.OrderErrorMessage] as string;
}

<div class="container py-4">
    <div class="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center mb-4">
        <div>
            <h1 class="h3 mb-0 fw-bold text-dark">Quản lý Đơn hàng</h1>
            <p class="text-muted small mb-0">Theo dõi và quản lý các đơn hàng của khách hàng.</p>
        </div>
        <a asp-action="Create" class="btn btn-primary px-4 py-2 rounded-3 shadow-sm">
            <i class="bi bi-plus-lg me-1"></i> Tạo đơn hàng mới
        </a>
    </div>

    @if (!string.IsNullOrEmpty(successMessage))
    {
        <div class="alert alert-success alert-dismissible fade show alert-global mb-3" role="alert">
            <i class="bi bi-check-circle-fill me-2"></i>@successMessage
            <button type="button" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="alert"></button>
        </div>
    }
    @if (!string.IsNullOrEmpty(errorMessage))
    {
        <div class="alert alert-warning alert-dismissible fade show alert-global mb-3" role="alert">
            <i class="bi bi-exclamation-triangle-fill me-2"></i>@errorMessage
            <button type="button" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="alert"></button>
        </div>
    }

    <!-- Filters & Search -->
    <div class="card border-0 shadow-sm rounded-4 mb-4">
        <div class="card-body p-3">
            <partial name="_Search" model="@(new OrderListSearchModel { Keywords = Model.Keywords, Status = Model.Status })" />
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Orders Table -->
    <div class="card border-0 shadow-sm rounded-4 overflow-hidden">
        <div class="card-body p-0">
            <div class="table-responsive">
                <table class="table table-hover align-middle mb-0">
                    <thead class="bg-light text-muted small text-uppercase">
                        <tr>
                            <th class="ps-3" style="width: 15%">
                                <span class="d-none d-lg-inline">Mã đơn hàng</span>
                                <span class="d-inline d-lg-none">Mã</span>
                            </th>
                            <th>Khách hàng</th>
                            <th class="text-end">Tổng tiền</th>
                            <th class="text-center">Ngày giao</th>
                            <th class="text-center">Trạng thái</th>
                            <th class="text-end pe-3"></th>
                        </tr>
                    </thead>
                    <tbody>
                        @if (Model.Data.Pagination.TotalCount > 0)
                        {
                            @foreach (var item in Model.Data)
                            {
                                <tr>
                                    <td class="ps-4">
                                        <span class="fw-600 text-primary d-block text-nowrap">@HighlighHelper.Highlight(item.Code, query)</span>
                                        <span class="small text-muted">@item.CreatedOn.ToString(ViewConstants.DefaultDateTimeFormat)</span>
                                    </td>
                                    <td>
                                        <div class="d-flex align-items-center">
                                            <div class="bg-light rounded-circle p-2 me-2 d-none d-lg-block">
                                                <i class="bi bi-person"></i>
                                            </div>
                                            <div>
                                                <div class="fw-600 text-nowrap">
                                                    @HighlighHelper.Highlight(item.CustomerName, query)
                                                </div>
                                                @if (!string.IsNullOrEmpty(item.CustomerPhone))
                                                {
                                                    <div>
                                                        <a href="tel:@item.CustomerPhone" class="text-muted small text-decoration-none text-nowrap">
                                                            <i class="bi bi-telephone me-1"></i> @HighlighHelper.Highlight(item.CustomerPhone, query)
                                                        </a>
                                                    </div>
                                                }
                                                @if (!string.IsNullOrEmpty(item.CustomerAddress))
                                                {
                                                    var encodedAddress = MyUrlEncoder.Encode(item.CustomerAddress);
                                                    <div>
                                                        <a href="https://www.google.com/maps/search/@encodedAddress" target="_blank" class="text-muted small text-decoration-none">
                                                            <span class="d-none d-lg-inline">
                                                                <i class="bi bi-geo-alt me-1"></i>
                                                                @HighlighHelper.Highlight(item.CustomerAddress, query)
                                                            </span>
                                                            <span class="text-nowrap d-inline d-lg-none">
                                                                <i class="bi bi-geo-alt me-1"></i>
                                                                @HighlighHelper.Highlight(item.CustomerAddress.Substring(0, int.Min(30, item.CustomerAddress.Length)), query)
                                                                @if (item.CustomerAddress.Length > 30)
                                                                {
                                                                    @:...
                                                                }
                                                            </span>
                                                        </a>
                                                    </div>
                                                }
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                    </td>
                                    <td class="text-end text-nowrap">
                                        @item.TotalAmount.ToString("N0") @ViewConstants.DefaultCurrencySymbol
                                    </td>
                                    <td class="text-center text-muted">
                                        <span class="text-nowrap">
                                            @item.ExpectedShippingDate.ToString(ViewConstants.DefaultDateFormat)
                                        </span>
                                    </td>
                                    <td class="text-center">
                                        <div class="d-flex justify-content-center gap-1 flex-wrap">
                                            <span class="badge rounded-pill @GetStatusBadgeClass(item.Status) px-2 py-1 fw-normal" title="Đơn hàng">
                                                <i class="bi bi-box-seam me-1"></i> @GetStatusText(item.Status)
                                            </span>
                                            <span class="badge rounded-pill @GetPaymentStatusBadgeClass(item.PaymentStatus) px-2 py-1 fw-normal d-none d-lg-inline" title="Thanh toán">
                                                <i class="bi bi-wallet2 me-1"></i> @GetPaymentStatusText(item.PaymentStatus)
                                            </span>
                                            <span class="badge rounded-pill @GetShippingStatusBadgeClass(item.ShippingStatus) px-2 py-1 fw-normal d-none d-lg-inline" title="Vận chuyển">
                                                <i class="bi bi-truck me-1"></i> @GetShippingStatusText(item.ShippingStatus)
                                            </span>
                                        </div>
                                    </td>
                                    <td class="text-end pe-4">
                                        <button class="btn btn-sm btn-light border-0 ms-1 rounded-circle" type="button" data-bs-toggle="dropdown">
                                            <i class="bi bi-three-dots"></i>
                                        </button>
                                        <ul class="dropdown-menu dropdown-menu-end shadow-sm border-0">
                                            <li>
                                                @if (item.CanUpdateInfo)
                                                {
                                                    <a class="dropdown-item" asp-action="Details" asp-route-id="@item.Id">
                                                        <i class="bi bi-pencil-square me-2"></i>
                                                        Chỉnh sửa
                                                    </a>
                                                }
                                                else
                                                {
                                                    <a class="dropdown-item" asp-action="Details" asp-route-id="@item.Id">
                                                        <i class="bi bi-eye me-2"></i>
                                                        Xem
                                                    </a>
                                                }
                                            </li>
                                            <li><hr class="dropdown-divider"></li>
                                            <li>
                                                <button class="dropdown-item text-danger btnDelete" data-code="@item.Code">
                                                    <i class="bi bi-trash me-2"></i>
                                                    Xóa đơn
                                                </button>
                                            </li>
                                        </ul>
                                    </td>
                                </tr>
                            }
                        }
                        else
                        {
                            <tr>
                                <td colspan="5" class="py-5 text-center text-muted">
                                    <div class="mb-2"><i class="bi bi-inbox fs-1 opacity-25"></i></div>
                                    Không tìm thấy đơn hàng nào phù hợp.
                                </td>
                            </tr>
                        }
                    </tbody>

                </table>
            </div>
            @if (Model.Data.Pagination.TotalCount > 0)
            {
                <partial name="_Pager" model="Model.Data.Pagination" />
            }

        </div>
    </div>
</div>
@foreach (var item in Model.Data)
{
    <partial name="_DeleteForm" model="@item.Id" />
}
@section Scripts {
    <script type="module" defer>
        import { confirm } from "/modules/modals.js";
        (function () {
        $('.btnDelete').on('click', async function (e) {
        e.preventDefault();
        const code = $(this).data('code');
        $(this).prop('disabled', true);
        const confirmed = await confirm('Xóa đơn hàng', `Bạn muốn xóa đơn hàng <strong>${code}</strong>?`);
        if (!confirmed) { $(this).prop('disabled', false); return; }
        $(`#deleteForm${$(this).data('id')}`).submit();
        });
        })();
    </script>
}

